    {
      "text": "Adidas Power Soccer is a 1996 association football video game developed and published by Psygnosis for the PlayStation and Microsoft Windows. The game, sponsored by German sportswear company Adidas, is the first in the Adidas Power Soccer series, and spawned the sequels Adidas Power Soccer International 97 and Adidas Power Soccer 98.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Adidas Power Soccer è un videogioco di calcio sviluppato e pubblicato dalla Psygnosis per PlayStation e Microsoft Windows nel 1996.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Adidas Power Soccer』は、1996年にPsygnosisによってPlayStationおよびMicrosoft Windows向けに開発・発売されたアソシエーション・フットボールのビデオゲームである。ドイツのスポーツウェア会社アディダスがスポンサーとなった本作は、『Adidas Power Soccer』シリーズの初代作品であり、続編となる『Adidas Power Soccer International 97』や『Adidas Power Soccer 98』を生み出した。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
